Hi! I'm VSE from the phpBB community.

Welcome to my Github repository for my MODs for phpBB3.

*
* Precise Similar Topics II v1.1.0
* ========================================================================
*
* Description:
* This MOD will display a list of similar/related topics at the bottom of
* your threads, based on finding the most relevant Topic Titles.
*
* ************************************************************************
* IMPORTANT NOTICE:
* IF YOU ARE GOING TO UPDATE FROM A VERSION PRIOR TO v1.1.0:
* YOU MUST FULLY UNINSTALL THE OLD VERSION - UNDO ANY OF THE FILE EDITS
* AND RUN THE "UNINSTALL" OPTION IN THE INSTALL_SIMILAR_TOPICS.PHP FILE.
* THEN YOU CAN INSTALL THE NEW VERSION 1.1.0
* ************************************************************************
*
* To-do list:
* Just keep testing ;)
